trans-unit.source: Serves as a base class for readers of incoming request parameters for Web services implemented using HTTP but without SOAP.
trans-unit.target: Fungerer som en basisklasse for lesere av innkommende forespørselsparametere for webtjenester implementert ved hjelp av HTTP, men uten SOAP.

trans-unit.source: ValueCollectionParameterReader and other classes in the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols> namespace support the .NET Framework's implementations of Web services via the HTTP-GET and HTTP-POST operations.
trans-unit.target: ValueCollectionParameterReader og andre klasser i den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols>navneområdet støtter .NET Framework-implementeringer av webtjenester via HTTP-GET og HTTP-POST-operasjoner.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols>

trans-unit.source: Web service writers and readers serialize and deserialize, respectively, between the parameters or return objects of Web methods and the HTTP request or response streams.
trans-unit.target: Web service forfattere lesere serialisere og deserialisere henholdsvis mellom parameterne eller return objekter av Web-metoder og HTTP-forespørselen eller svar dataflytene.

trans-unit.source: Web service writers and readers use HTTP for transport but don't exchange messages using the SOAP standard.
trans-unit.target: Web service forfattere og lesere bruke HTTP til transport, men exchange ikke meldinger ved hjelp av SOAP-standard.

trans-unit.source: The ValueCollectionParameterReader class provides, among other methods, a common <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader.Read%2A> method for all service-side readers of collections of name/value pairs into Web method parameters.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ValueCollectionParameterReader gir, blant andre metoder et felles <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader.Read%2A>metode for alle serversiden lesere med samlinger av navn/verdi-par til Web-metodeparametere.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader.Read%2A>

trans-unit.source: The name/value pairs have been parsed from an incoming HTTP request.
trans-unit.target: Navn/verdi-par analysert fra en innkommende HTTP-forespørsel.

trans-unit.source: You typically will not need to use ValueCollectionParameterReader or its descendant classes directly.
trans-unit.target: Du trenger vanligvis ikke å bruke ValueCollectionParameterReader eller de underordnede klassene direkte.

trans-unit.source: The appropriate types are used according to settings in an ASP.NET configuration file (Web.config).
trans-unit.target: De ønskede typene som brukes i samsvar med innstillingene i en ASP.NET-konfigurasjonsfil (Web.config).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Returns an initializer for the specified method.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en initialisering for den angitte metoden.

trans-unit.source: The object returned by the GetInitializer method is the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo.InParameters%2A> property of the `methodinfo` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Objektet som ble returnert av metoden GetInitializer er den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo.InParameters%2A>for den `methodinfo` parameteren.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo.InParameters%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo.InParameters%2A> property value is an array of type <xref:System.Reflection.ParameterInfo>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo.InParameters%2A>Egenskapsverdien er en matrise av typen <xref:System.Reflection.ParameterInfo>.</xref:System.Reflection.ParameterInfo> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo.InParameters%2A>

trans-unit.source: The GetInitializer method is invoked during service initialization.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetInitializer aktiveres under initialisering av tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: Later, at the time a request is processed, the initializer object is passed to the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader.Initialize%2A> method of another <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader> instance.
trans-unit.target: Senere, når en forespørsel behandles, initialisering-objektet er sendt til den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader.Initialize%2A>-metoden til et annet <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader>forekomsten.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader.Initialize%2A>

trans-unit.source: The other instance performs the actual reading.
trans-unit.target: Den andre forekomsten utfører den faktiske lesing.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo"></xref> that specifies the Web method for which the initializer is obtained.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo"> </xref> som angir Web-metoden i initialisering hentes.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo"></xref> representing the Web method.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo"> </xref> som representerer Web-metoden.

trans-unit.source: Initializes an instance.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en forekomst.

trans-unit.source: The Initialize method is invoked at the time a request is processed.
trans-unit.target: I initialiseringsmetoden aktiveres når en forespørselen behandles.

trans-unit.source: The input parameter, `o`, is obtained by calling the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader.GetInitializer%2A> method on another instance during service initialization.
trans-unit.target: Inndataparameteren `o`, hentes ved å ringe det <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader.GetInitializer%2A>-metode på en annen forekomst under initialisering av tjenesten.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader.GetInitializer%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Reflection.ParameterInfo> array, obtained through the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo.InParameters*> property of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Reflection.ParameterInfo>matrise, fra den <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo.InParameters*>for den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo"> </xref> klasse.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo.InParameters*> </xref:System.Reflection.ParameterInfo>

trans-unit.source: Determines whether a particular parameter type is supported by the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer om en bestemt Parametertypen som støttes av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Reflection.ParameterInfo> that specifies the parameter to check.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Reflection.ParameterInfo>som angir parameteren til å kontrollere.</xref:System.Reflection.ParameterInfo>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if a method's parameter definitions are supported by the reader; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis en metode parameterdefinisjoner som støttes av leseren; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether a method definition's parameter definitions are supported by the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer om en metodedefinisjon parameterdefinisjoner som støttes av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo"></xref> that specifies the method to check.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.Services.Protocols.LogicalMethodInfo"> </xref> som angir metoden som skal se.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if a method's parameter definitions are supported by the reader; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis en metode parameterdefinisjoner som støttes av leseren; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Translates a collection of name/value pairs into an array of objects representing method parameter values.
trans-unit.target: Oversetter et antall navn/verdi-par til en matrise av objekter som representerer metoden parameterverdier.

trans-unit.source: The Read method is called by the Read method defined in thetwo classes derived from <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader>, <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.UrlParameterReader> and <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HtmlFormParameterReader>.
trans-unit.target: Metoden lese kalles av Read-metoden som er definert i to klasser som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader>, <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.UrlParameterReader>og <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HtmlFormParameterReader>.</xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.HtmlFormParameterReader> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.UrlParameterReader> </xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.ValueCollectionParameterReader>

trans-unit.source: Those two classes' Read methods take an <xref:System.Web.HttpRequest> parameter.
trans-unit.target: Disse to klasser lese metoder ta en <xref:System.Web.HttpRequest>parameter.</xref:System.Web.HttpRequest>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.NameValueCollection"></xref> object that specifies the collection of name/value pairs containing method parameter names and values.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Collections.Specialized.NameValueCollection"> </xref> objekt som angir samlingen av navn/verdi-par med metoden parameternavn og verdier.

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref:System.Object> objects representing method parameter values.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref:System.Object>objekter som representerer metoden parameterverdier.</xref:System.Object>
